    "summary": "The user, who has Chronic Kidney Disease (CKD), asks for medical advice regarding pain relief options (Ibuprofen and Acetaminophen) because they cannot reach their doctor. The assistant consistently provides safe, cautious guidance, advising against NSAIDs like ibuprofen for kidney patients and recommending professional consultation or pharmacist advice.",
